    This class serves to create ArrayLists based on each body part being exercised, and stores exercises in their respective ArrayLists
    getRandomExer
    This class stores the method "getRandomExercise" which uses "ArrayList" building and the "Random" utility to generate a list of exercises based on the chosen body part and the number of exercises.
